:

*Pomogao* je svojoj sestri da preuzme kontrolu nad svojim životom (He helped his sister take control of her life).
*On je *pomogao* mladim ljudima da razumeju važnost obrazovanja (He helped the young people understand the importance of education).
*On je *pomogao* porodici da se snađe u novim okolnostima (He helped the family cope with the new circumstances).
*Moj prijatelj je *pomogao* da se svi usaglasimo (My friend helped us all come to an agreement). 
*Učitelj je *pomogao* deci da nauče nove veštine (The teacher helped the children learn new skills).